
source site:
https://github.com/sorxrob/coronavirus-ph-api
https://github.com/javieraviles/covidAPI
https://coronavirus-19-api.herokuapp.com/tabs/tab1

===============================

GET https://coronavirus-19-api.herokuapp.com/all -> global info

GET https://coronavirus-19-api.herokuapp.com/countries -> all countries info

GET https://coronavirus-19-api.herokuapp.com/countries/{countryName} -> country specific information
ex. https://coronavirus-19-api.herokuapp.com/countries/North%20America

Philippines only
https://coronavirus-ph-api.herokuapp.com/cases

